      Deprecated. 
      use ofClassPathAndJavaRuntime instead
      static ClassResolver ClassResolver.ofClassPathAndJavaRuntime()
      Creates a ClassResolver with all entries for ofClassPath() and all entries from the sun.boot.class.path system-properties for java 8 and before or all java runtime modules from Java 9 on.

      Creates a ClassResolver similar to ofClassPath(), but without the entries from the Class-Path attribute of any Manifest file.
      static ClassResolver ClassResolver.ofClassPathWithoutJars()
      Creates a ClassResolver containing only the directories on the java.class.path system-property.
